                     <incipit>Expulsus </incipit>
                     <explicit><note>(ends impf.)</note> ita et opus tuum nam unde saluas </explicit>
                     <note>From Merton Coll. 58. c. 8, the same leaf as art. 4.</note>
                     <note>Allen, <title>Richard Rolle</title>, p. 63, q. v. for early printed editions.</note>
                  </msItem>
